        {
            "title": "全日收市︱持續調整 恒指跌32點報22944點 芯片股氣勢勁 恒生績後受壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午後持續調整，主板成交進一步縮至2625.67億元。芯片股氣勢如虹，業績股表現暫較遜色，恒生(00011)更成藍籌包尾。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數經過昨天於23000點得而復失後，今早低開199點後初段進一步尋底，跌幅曾擴大至327點，低見22649點，其後迅速由谷底反彈，中段跌幅一度收窄至僅跌1點，衝上22975點，只是暫欠再彈動力，其後大部份時間在跌幅約210點以內徘徊；恒指最後收報22944點，跌32點或0.14%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數繼續跑贏大市，今早開市後約45分鐘已開始倒升，其後進入好淡爭持局面，收報5672點，升33點或0.59%；國企指數則跌12點或0.15%，報8463點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14717961-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e6%8c%81%e7%ba%8c%e8%aa%bf%e6%95%b4-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c32%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b122944%e9%bb%9e-%e8%8a%af%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e6%b0%a3%e5%8b%a2%e5%8b%81",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-web_HKStock-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-19 16:20:52",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股收升創板升逾2%  機器人及晶片股揚",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股全日報升，兩市成交合計17210.19億元(人民幣‧下同)，創板升逾2%，晶片股及機器人股受捧。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指全日報3351點，升27點或0.81%，近全日高位收市，今早以3320點開市，跌3點或0.11%，為全日低位，隨即節節上升，最高見3352點，升28點或0.84%，午後續向好，全日成交6751.46億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指全日報10772點，升155點或1.46%，今早開市報10592點，亦跌25點或0.24%，最低見10588，跌29點或0.27%，為全日低位，午後升破上午高位，高見10774，升124點彧1.17%，全日成交10458.73億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數全日報3940點，升27點或0.7%，今早跌6點或0.17%，開報3906點；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日報2226點，升44點或2.03%，今早開市報2174點，跌7點或0.35%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">晶片股及人形機器人股揚升，華虹半導體(688347.SH)飆17.96%，報60.28元 ; 中芯(688981.SH)升3.72%，報101.94元 ; 上海復旦(688385.SH)升8.29%，報43元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">人形機器人概念揚升，平治信息(300571.SZ)收升20%，報37.2元、漢威科技(300007.SZ)升19.99%，報37.81元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14717718-a%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%87%e5%89%b5%e6%9d%bf%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be2-%e6%a9%9f%e5%99%a8%e4%ba%ba%e5%8f%8a%e6%99%b6%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e6%8f%9a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230629_FI_A%E8%82%A1_9_source-ap_.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-19 15:20:55",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "恒生去年底不良貸款比率6.12% 仍料信貸損失提撥按年可降24%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生銀行(00011)去年底時不良貸款比率達6.12%，但恒生行政總裁施穎茵相信，信貸損失提撥仍可按年減24%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：恒生銀行官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230705-155929_source-web_恒生銀行_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：恒生銀行官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230705-155929_source-web_恒生銀行_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：恒生銀行官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">她在業績記者會上表示，高息環境持續，為一些香港商業地產客戶帶來現金流壓力，當中部份客戶要求延遲還款，是導致恒生去年底不良貸款比率上升的原因之一。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">不過她指出，銀行有三分之二貸款有提供充足抵押品作擔保，無擔保貸款的質素亦保持穩定。市場普遍預期今年有望減息兩次，每次減25點子，望能紓緩企業現金流壓力，為本地地產信貸帶來改善。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">有券商對恒生未再提新一輪回購感失望。恒生財務總監蘇雪冰在記者會上被問及銀行會不推出新一輪回購計畫時表示，回購是回報股東的選擇之一，恒生將繼續考慮不同方法回報股東。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14717583-%e6%81%92%e7%94%9f%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e5%ba%95%e4%b8%8d%e8%89%af%e8%b2%b8%e6%ac%be%e6%af%94%e7%8e%876-12-%e4%bb%8d%e6%96%99%e4%bf%a1%e8%b2%b8%e6%90%8d%e5%a4%b1%e6%8f%90%e6%92%a5%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240723_FI_source-web_00011.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-19 15:00:49",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日股險守39000點關 收市微跌0.27%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日股全日走勢偏弱，日經平均指數曾短暫失守39000點關口，低見38994點；收報39164點，微跌105點或0.27%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14717528-%e6%97%a5%e8%82%a1%e9%9a%aa%e5%ae%8839000%e9%bb%9e%e9%97%9c-%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%e5%be%ae%e8%b7%8c0-27",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240826_FI_source-ap_Japan_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-19 14:40:43",
